    <para>
     <function>OCIStatementType</function> returns on of the following values:
     <orderedlist>
      <listitem><simpara>			"SELECT"
      <listitem><simpara>			"UPDATE"
      <listitem><simpara>			"DELETE"
      <listitem><simpara>			"INSERT"
      <listitem><simpara>			"CREATE"
